Visual composer shortcodes appearing in various posts in latest version of wordpress

This is a problem troubling many of the developers and people spend many hours to solve it.

There is an easy way to stop it... Yes really...

The short codes are appearing beacause of editing the page with visual composer. Go to the settings of the visual composer plugin and 
uncheck the type of post , in which you are having trouble. now go to that particular post and try to edit it with native editor. You
can find the short codes appearing there as text. Remove it from the editor and save.. 

Thats all.. The issue is solved..
